                  <pb xml:id="DLCL_CF_E10059_A01_C1R" n="1 - Recto" facs="https://classense.unibo.it/files/large/21140/DSC_5939.jpg"/>
                  
                  <p>
                     <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0101">Europa Orientale</placeName>  
                     <foreign xml:lang="la">
                        Ex Jo. Jansionii Abl. Amst. 1647 in folio Maj. 
                        Pagina 17 Moscovin, sive <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0102">Russia</placeName> Alba <del rend="overstrike">pag</del>. folio 17. 
                        <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0102">Russia</placeName> vel late vel presse sumitur. 
                        Late ipsam quoque <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0103">Poloniam</placeName> et <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0104">Lituaniam</placeName> complectitur. 
                        Presse in <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0102">Russiam</placeName> Nigram et Albam distinguitur. 
                        Nigra inter Poloniam Minorem, Voliniam, <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0104">Lituaniam,</placeName> <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0103">Polodiam,</placeName> 
                        <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0105">Moldaviam,</placeName> <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0106">Transilvaniam,</placeName> 
                        et <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0100">Hungariam</placeName> sita est. 
                        Polonis dicta Czarna <hi rend="underline">Rusz</hi> ad differentiam Majoris sive Albae. 
                        Latine Russos et Ruthenos vocant incolas, quos [aRoxolanis] originem atque nomen habere, putant. 
                        Suos aliquando habuit Duces, postmodum Poloniae Regno adi<del rend="overstrike">en</del>ucta. 
                        <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0102">Russia</placeName> Alba sive Major Moscovitici Imperij pars est omnium <placeName ref="#DLCL_CF_L0061">Europae</placeName> Regionum 
                        vastissima inculta ac paludibus silvisque invia <hi rend="underline">Moscovia</hi> a capite suo dicta. 
                     </foreign>
                  </p>
                  
                  <pb xml:id="DLCL_CF_E10059_A01_C1V" n="1 - Verso" facs="https://classense.unibo.it/files/large/21140/DSC_5940.jpg"/>
                  
